I know Ramulus is at the Ark, so is SnowCat.

Spears::

She pulled her hand back and looked at Striker, "Chip? What chip? I 
belong to Master Prebon. Please do as he says. I don't want you to 
get hurt. Please just let him earase your memory of this place. Your 
experiance here hasn't been pleasent. I don't want you to think of 
this place. Please just so as he says."

The chip had made her forget about the chip even being on her.  She 
looked at Striker and sighed. "If you continue to struggle, you'll 
only be caused pain. Please don't do that. Ramulus is expecting you 
in good condition."   She gave him a weak smile.
